data.description:
Back on Market!
Single Story Highland Home with over 2500 sq ft. featuring 4 bedroom, Study, 2 Bath. Soaring 10ft Ceilings, large kitchen, Large Master. Close to retail and restaurants. Lake Lewisville and Little Elm beach are just a 10 minute drive. Home right on the border of Frisco and all it's amenities like The world HQ of the Dallas Cowboys, The Star, Toyota Stadium and more. Come bring your decorative ideas and make this your home.  Schedule your tour today 469-815-5146.
